{"tid":2147101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：民主黨阻礙落實紓困措施及刺激國家經濟方案","createTime":"2020-08-09T04:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T04:32:28.000Z","uid":200758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"53e2e5bcfd8ea719e3429f28b29b5be2a7305bde","tid":2147101,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:30:07.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】特朗普政府與民主黨仍未能就新一輪新冠病毒紓困方案達成共識，總統特朗普決定簽署行政命令繞過國會延長部分紓困措施。<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n白宮官員與民主黨領袖就延長紓困措施談判了近兩周，但仍未能達成共識。雙方在失業救濟金金額等問題上有分歧，民主黨要求將金額維持在每周六百美元，不過白宮認為金額太高，會減低民眾求職意欲。民主黨的眾議院議長佩洛西批評特朗普做法，又指州政府缺乏資金，無力支付救濟金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=401037&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401037%26refer%3DShare&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=d7f44095\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401037%26refer%3DShare&h=c464153e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=401037&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"9b301d09c1ffea050dc09f503487563333460824","tid":2147101,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:32:27.000Z","msg":"正喎每個星期4800蚊洗鬼出去做野咩，日日留係屋企打機啦！"},{"pid":"38d0419cf772755dfda081ebfceabdb40b0bde35","tid":2147101,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}